release.changelog:
Here's what's new this week:
* The ad blocker has been accelerated and memory usage optimized. It's no longer in Beta.
* A Tracker blocker (Beta) has been added to prevent tracking scripts on websites. It needs to be enabled from the settings.
* The issue of certain site icons not displaying on the home screen shortcuts, bookmarks, and history pages has been fixed.
* The design of the subscriptions page has been updated, and a lifetime license tab has been added.
